    "causal_summary": "The code-graph doc lane is hash-only: `'doc'` is excluded from the tree-sitter parser type (`tree-sitter-parser.ts:67` `type ParserLanguage = Exclude<SupportedLanguage,'doc'>`), and when `language === 'doc'` the indexer short-circuits to an empty result (`structural-indexer.ts:1237-1249` returns `{nodes:[], edges:[], contentHash, parseHealth:'clean'…}`)",
